fields.name: Digests
fields.description: Advisor digest configuration. Valid only for subscriptions

fields.name: Duration
fields.description: Minimum duration for Advisor low CPU utilization evaluation. Valid only for subscriptions. Valid values: 7 (default), 14, 21, 30, 60 or 90.

fields.name: Exclude
fields.description: Exclude the resource from Advisor evaluations. Valid values: False (default) or True.

fields.name: LowCPUThreshold
fields.description: Minimum percentage threshold for Advisor low CPU utilization evaluation. Valid only for subscriptions. Valid values: 5 (default), 10, 15 or 20.
